{"tid":2454193,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭博：投行不滿林鄭送檢政策 擬局部撤走","createTime":"2021-03-20T05:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T04:58:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d0afa29a50edf66fe6eb788ae8fb029ccf473c80","tid":2454193,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:00:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210320/Y36P2HIK3FELBNDWLA4YIGKKJQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210320%2FY36P2HIK3FELBNDWLA4YIGKKJQ%2F&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=293151af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210320%2FY36P2HIK3FELBNDWLA4YIGKKJQ%2F&h=39335f9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210320/Y36P2HIK3FELBNDWLA4YIGKKJQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n彭博：投行不滿林鄭送檢政策 擬局部撤走<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港疫情反覆，近日西營盤健身室群組爆疫更衝擊香港金融界核心地帶，政府抗疫措施亦惹來金融業人士不滿。彭博引述一名國際投行高層指，如果香港長期維持現行的隔離檢疫政策，公司不得不考慮將部份交易員，轉移至其他金融中心。報道指政府昨日與國際商會等商界組織會晤，講解最新的疫情情況。政務司長辦公室未回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港首宗 66歲男打BNT後亡  17歲青年接種即腹痛失知覺送院<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隔離營WiFi差難工作<br />\n<br />\n報道引述國際投行高層稱，公司擔心一旦員工或其家屬被列為確診者的密切接觸者，即使檢測呈陰性，亦要入住檢疫中心兩星期，但指定檢疫地的房內設施不足、WiFi連接亦差，交易員與團隊會突然中斷聯絡。另一間國際金融公司的管理層亦擔心，隨着疫苗加快推出，其他城市陸續放寬封關限制，倘若香港繼續現行檢疫措施，將不利他們挽留及吸引海外人才。<br />\n<br />\n報道又引述知情人士透露，有。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：藍田主婦抱孫往潮福播毒 食客中招<br />\n<br />\n金利豐證券研究部執行董事黃德几表示，不少銀行早已實施在家工作，雖然證券。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n西營盤URSUS Fitness群組直至昨日已經累積有138人染疫，不少都是金融界人士，中環滙豐總行大廈共有三人確診，該行被納入強制。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cS-Y4IDW6kgbKO_Z072f-sQIHto=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ND6ECY3MEJGHHPG6W2NDZSPGPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcS-Y4IDW6kgbKO_Z072f-sQIHto%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FND6ECY3MEJGHHPG6W2NDZSPGPE.jpg&h=138a9c59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■疫情近日擴散至中環金融區，惟政府檢疫措施惹業界不滿。"},{"pid":"691fe90811c96debb4948888c6be0d8e128d3c4e","tid":2454193,"uid":80,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:11:41.000Z","msg":"扮咩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國安法落實都唔走"},{"pid":"d5a58f4cf560ee3ebada4e4ec5589b00923f2edb","tid":2454193,"uid":269481,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f1tZLq6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff1tZLq6.png&h=1b72199a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc8cf627dd1abe1e4450a466b629c4f7c1d910a0","tid":2454193,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:25:30.000Z","msg":"連登仔話唔番公司都冇影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c62433e470d056a9b62dcc8e951d436a82706fc","tid":2454193,"uid":72630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"基本法腐乳.jpg"},{"pid":"be789ff94a28da2291865f143c6bc26e8399b757","tid":2454193,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T04:54:45.000Z","msg":"港獨華呢？"},{"pid":"c54369a06a0f8608490bf7b835f593fb898dbbe2","tid":2454193,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"691fe90811c96debb4948888c6be0d8e128d3c4e","tid":2454193,"uid":80,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:11:41.000Z","msg":"扮咩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國安法落實都唔走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T04:58:20.000Z","msg":"根本係借口黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}